<h2 class="section-cv">Pierre Lassalle</h2>
<p class="leading">
I am currently preparing a Ph.D. at the <a href="http://www.cesbio.ups-tlse.fr/">CESBIO</a> 
laboratory in Toulouse in France where I am performing research on the processing of 
large remote sensing images. My research focuses mainly on the scalability of
segmentation and classification algorithms for large multitemporal
series of high resolution images.
</p>
